{"id": "pos044", "name": "Audio_St08_702_11_14", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Kenta, is anyone outside?</font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "No one in sight! They're all at the front door!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Shh! Too loud!</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "It's okay, NEKO. The front door is quite far away from here. The sound won't travel that far... Let's wait for Kouhei here.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "I'm sorry... for causing you guys all this trouble...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Aroma-chan, you need to stop apologizing!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "NEKO's right. This is really all the help we can offer you too... Hope you can remember more things after you get to that bar...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Yes...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Ummm... Miss PAFF...</font>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Ah, your name is... Kenta, right? What's the matter?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "Miss PAFF... Can I have your autograph?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "This is... my album?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Ha!? Ya little brat, when did you buy this... and this one of all things! The album where the Mono bastards cheated NEKO out of all the songs I wrote!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">I just like this one the most... Big sister's songs are all so good...</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "NEKO... Can I sign it?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Umm... Y... yeah, you can.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Marker_Pen_sign", "Signs"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Here, Kenta.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "Thank you, Miss PAFF... Kenta, remember to say thank you.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "T, thank you, Miss PAFF!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "NEKO... That album, Mono purposely chose to not put your name on it... You were right to be angry. I am really sorry.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "... Oh that. Nah, it's fine. No big deal... So you did find out?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "My sister just told me that it's company policy. I only knew about the details later when I asked Chris about it... What they did was awful. I've always wanted to properly apologize to you. You wrote such amazing songs too...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "I, it's not Aroma-chan's fault either! The ones that deserve the blame are Chris and the other idiots at Mono! It was also kinda NEKO's fault since I did spew a lot of random crap back then. Xenon chewed out NEKO for the same reason too ahahaha!\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Thank you... NEKO's music really is amazing. If I have the opportunity, I would love to sing for NEKO's songs again.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "For real? Of course I'm down for that! Once Aroma-chan remembers everything, NEKO will write a few more awesome songs for you to sing! And we will have a collab with Xenon, ah, and Sis Cherry too... Hehe, maybe we can even get ROBO to organize a LIVE for everyone!\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "S...sure. Haha.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Hoho~ Is this what it feels like to get carried?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Carried? What does that mean...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Elevator_Alert", "Alarm"], "content": ""}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Men In Black"], "content": "Unit A has located the target. Initiate apprehend operation immediately.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "Big sister! So many people!!\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Yikes! What are you people trying to do!?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Men In Black"], "content": "... Miss Aroma White, we are here to pick you up. Please don't resist. We promise that we won't use any violence.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "M... me?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "You people... aren't Miss PAFF's fans, I suppose? Where are you trying to take Miss PAFF to?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Men In Black"], "content": "This has nothing to do with outsiders. Please step away.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Who's gonna let you suspicious folks take Aroma-chan away! She still has to sing NEKO's new songs! NEKO's gonna i, inform the admins!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Men In Black"], "content": "... Apprehend the target.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "R... run! Aroma-chan!\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "O, okay!\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Men In Black"], "content": "You're not getting away. Go after her! Surround them!\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_horn", "Honking"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "That's... daddy? It's daddy's car!!\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "Engine Sounds"], "content": ""}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Aroma-chan, get in the car!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Ah... U, understood!</font>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">健太、外に人は？</font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "いないよ！みんな玄関の方にいるみたい！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">しーっ！バカ！声が大きい！</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "大丈夫よ。\nここは玄関からは遠いわ。\n向こうまで声は届かないはず……\nここで車を待ちましょう。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "ご迷惑をおかけして……すみません……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "もう謝らなくていいから！ね！Aromaっち！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "そうよ。\n私たちにはこれくらしかできないもの……\nバーに着いてから、もっといろいろなことを思い出せるといいわね。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "はい……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">あの……PAFFお姉ちゃん……</font>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "あ……健太君……だよね？\nどうしたの？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "PAFFお姉ちゃん……サインしてくれる？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "これは……私のアルバム？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "はぁ！？\nクソガキ！いつの間にこんなもの……しかもよりによってこれ！\nMonoがNEKOを騙して書かせた曲が大量に入ってるやつじゃん！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">だって、これが一番好きなんだもん……\nお姉ちゃんの曲が好きだから……</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "NEKO……私、サインしてもいい？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "あ～……い、いいよ。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Marker_Pen_sign", "サイン"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "はい、健太くん。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "ありがとう、PAFFさん……健太お礼を言いなさい。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "あ、ありがとう！PAFFお姉ちゃん！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "NEKO……あの……このアルバムなんだけど、Monoがあなたの名前を載せなかったこと……本当に、ごめんなさい。\n嫌な気持ちにさせて、本当に本当にごめんなさい。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……あぁ、うん、そのことね……\n別に……うん。\n……てか、知ってたんだね。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "お姉ちゃんは会社の方針としか言ってくれなかったけど、あとからChrisに詳しい話を聞いたの。\nこんなの良くないことなのに……\nずっとあなたに謝りたかった。\nだってあなたの曲は素晴らしいもの。なのに……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "A……Aromaっちのせいじゃないし！\n最低なのはChrisたちでしょ！\nNEKOが調子に乗りすぎちゃうせいでこうなったようなもんだし！\nXenonにも怒られたことあるんだー！あははは！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "ありがとう……NEKOの曲は本当に素晴らしいと思う。\nまた、NEKOの曲を歌いたいな。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "ほんと？\nもちろんだよ！\nAromaっちの記憶のことが解決したら、NEKOが最高の曲をAromaっちに書くね！\nあとはXenonも誘って、あ！Cherryさんも！\nあとは～ROBOも誘ってライブしよ！\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん……うん！あはは。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "えへへ～キャリーってこんな感じか～\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "キャリー？なにそれ……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Elevator_Alert", "警報"], "content": ""}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["黒服の人"], "content": "A部隊ターゲットを確認。\n捕獲します。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "お姉ちゃん！たくさん人が来たよ！\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "わぁ！なに！？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["黒服の人"], "content": "……Aroma Whiteさん。お迎えに上がりました。\n無駄な抵抗はやめてください。\n手荒な真似はしません。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "私……私……？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "あなたたちはPAFFさんのファンの方ではありませんよね？\nPAFFさんをどこへ連れて行くつもりですか？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["黒服の人"], "content": "部外者には関係のないことだ。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "あんたらみたいな怪しい奴らにAromaっちを渡すわけないでしょ！\nAromaっちはNEKOの新曲を歌ってくれる約束もしてるんだから！\nNEKO、か……管理局に通報するよ！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["黒服の人"], "content": "……ターゲットを連れて行け。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "に……逃げるよ！Aromaっち！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "う、うん！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["黒服の人"], "content": "逃げられない。\n追え！逃げ場をふさぐんだ！\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_horn", "クラクション"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "あれは……パパ？パパの車だ！！\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "エンジン音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Aromaっち！乗るよ！</font>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">あ……う、うん！</font>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Kenta，外面有沒有人？</font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "沒有人！都在大門那邊！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">噓！小聲點！</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "不要緊，NEKO，大門離這裡很遠，聲音傳不過去的……我們就在這裡等 Kouhei 過來吧。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "抱歉……麻煩你們了……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "別再道歉了啦，Aroma 醬！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "是啊，我們也只能幫上這點忙而已……希望到了那間酒吧之後妳能想起更多事……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">那個……PAFF 姐姐……</font>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "啊，你叫……Kenta 對吧？怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "PAFF 姐姐……可以幫我簽名嗎？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "這是……我的專輯？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "哈！？臭小子，你什麼時候買的……而且還是這張！單聲狗騙 NEKO 寫了一大堆歌的專輯！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">人家最喜歡這張嘛……姊姊的歌好好聽……</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "NEKO……我可以簽嗎？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "呃……可……可以啦。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Marker_Pen_sign", "簽名"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "來，Kenta。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "謝謝妳，PAFF 小姐……Kenta，記得道謝喔。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "謝、謝謝 PAFF 姐姐！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "NEKO……那張專輯，單聲故意不掛妳的名字……害妳不高興，真的很對不起。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……那個喔，沒什麼啦……原來妳有發現？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊只和我說是公司政策，後來我才從 Chris 那裡問到詳細情況……這樣做很不好，我一直很想和妳好好道個歉，明明是那麼棒的歌……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "又、又不是 Aroma 醬的錯！亂搞的是 Chris 他們嘛！NEKO 也是太愛亂講話才會被弄啦，Xenon 明明也罵過 NEKO 的說，啊哈哈哈哈！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯，謝謝……NEKO 的音樂真的很棒，有機會的話，希望還能幫 NEKO 的曲子唱歌呢。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "真的嗎？當然好啊！等 Aroma 醬想起所有的事，NEKO 就再寫幾首超棒的歌給妳唱！還要找 Xenon 合作，啊，還有 Cherry 姐……欸嘿，找 ROBO 幫大家辦個 LIVE 好了！\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "好……好的，哈哈。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "欸嘿～這就是攀到大大的感覺吧？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "大大？那是什麼……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Elevator_Alert", "警報"], "content": ""}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["黑衣人"], "content": "A 部隊找到目標了，即刻展開捕捉行動。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "姊姊！好多人！！\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "哇！你們是幹什麼的！？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["黑衣人"], "content": "……Aroma White 小姐，我們是來接妳的。請不要抵抗，我們保證不會動粗。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "我……我？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "你們……應該不是 PAFF 小姐的粉絲吧？想把 PAFF 小姐帶去哪裡？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["黑衣人"], "content": "和外人無關，請讓開。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "誰會讓你們這些可疑的傢伙把 Aroma 醬帶走啊！她還要幫 NEKO 唱新歌耶！NEKO 要通、通報管理局囉！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["黑衣人"], "content": "……把目標帶走。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "快……快跑！Aroma 醬！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "好、好！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["黑衣人"], "content": "妳跑不掉的。追！把她們圍起來！\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_horn", "喇叭聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "那是……老爸？是老爸的車！！\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "引擎聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Aroma 醬，準備上車！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">啊……好、好的！</font>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Kenta, 바깥에 사람은?</font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "없어! 다들 대문 앞에만 있어!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">쉿! 큰 소리 내지 마 바보야!</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "너무 걱정할 필요 없어, NEKO. 대문에서 여긴 그래도 꽤 거리가 있으니까 저쪽에선 안 들릴 거야... 여기서 Kouhei가 올 때까지 기다리고 있자꾸나.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "죄송해요... 저 때문에...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "사과 좀 그만해, Aroma 짱!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "그래. 우리가 도와줄 수 있는 게 이것뿐이라... 그 술집에 도착하고 나서 네 기억도 많이 돌아왔으면 좋겠구나...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "네...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">저기... PAFF 누나...</font>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "아, 저... Kenta라고 했지? 왜 그러니?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "PAFF 누나... 사인 좀... 받아도... 될까요...?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "이건... 내 앨범?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "어랍쇼오오오!? 이 꼬맹이가! 너 이거 언제 산 거야? 게다가 이 앨범...!! 그 망할 모노 놈들이 NEKO가 쓴 곡을 속여서 만든 앨범이잖아!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">그래도 난 이 앨범이 가장 좋은 걸... 그래도 역시 누나가 만든 곡이 제일 듣기 좋단 말이야...</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "NEKO... 저, 사인해줘도 될까요?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "아... 어... 응...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Marker_Pen_sign", "사인"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "자, Kenta.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "고마워, PAFF...... Kenta, 감사하다고 해야지.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "가, 감사합니다! PAFF 누나!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "NEKO... 저... 모노가 고의로 NEKO의 이름을 빼버리고 발매한 앨범 일.... 정말 죄송해요...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "...아, 뭐 괜찮아... 너도 알고 있었어?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "언니가 그냥 저한테 회사 정책이 그렇다고만 얘기를 했었는데... 나중에 Chris 씨한테 물어봐서 자세한 상황을 듣게 됐어요... 그때부터 줄곧 NEKO한테 사과하고 싶었는데... 그렇게 좋은 음악을 만들어준 사람을...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "A... Aroma 짱 잘못이 아니야! 이건 전부 다 Chris랑 그 녀석들이 멋대로 저지른 일이라구! NEKO도 그때 심한 말을 좀 해서 그런 것도 있구! Xenon도 NEKO를 얼마나 혼냈는데! 하하하!\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "네, 고마워요... NEKO의 음악은 정말 최고예요. 기회가 생긴다면 계속해서 NEKO가 만든 노래를 불러보고 싶어요.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "정말이야? 문제 없쥐이이이! \nAroma 짱이 기억을 회복하고 나면, NEKO가 끝내주는 곡 몇 개 써줄게! Xenon 이랑 콜라보 한 곡도! 아, 그리고 Cherry 언니한테도 부탁해야겠구나! 그리고... 그렇지! ROBO한테도 LIVE 또 열어달라고 부탁해야지!\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "아... 알겠어요. 하하하.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "에헤헤~ 이게 바로 버스 캐리(carry)를 받는 자의 기분이란 건가~?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "캐...리? 그게 무슨 뜻이에요...?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Elevator_Alert", "경보"], "content": ""}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["검은 옷의 사내"], "content": "A 부대 목표 확인. \n체포를 시작한다.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kenta"], "content": "누나! 사람들이 엄청 많이!\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "우아앗! 너희들 다 뭐야!?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["검은 옷의 사내"], "content": "...Aroma White 씨, 당신을 모시러 왔습니다. 쓸데없는 저항은 삼가주시죠. 저희도 난폭하게 굴 생각은 없습니다.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "저... 저를요?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yukiko"], "content": "당신들은... PAFF의 팬이 아니군요? PAFF를 어디로 데려가려는 거죠?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["검은 옷의 사내"], "content": "외부인은 무관하다. 비켜라.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "누가 너희 같은 수상한 녀석들한테 Aroma 짱을 넘겨준대!? 애는 NEKO가 만든 신곡을 불러줘야 한다구! 과... 관리국에 신고해버릴 거야!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["검은 옷의 사내"], "content": "...목표를 데리고 돌아간다.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "도... 도망쳐! Aroma 짱!\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "아, 네!!\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["검은 옷의 사내"], "content": "도망칠 수 없습니다. 쫓아라! 저들을 전부 포위해!\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_horn", "클락션"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": 